commits.commit_title:
capi: Add blaze_symbolization_reason enum

This change introduces the blaze_symbolization_reason enumeration to
blazesym-c and adjusts the blaze_sym type to carry such a reason. We
also introduce the blaze_symbolization_reason_str() helper function
that can be used to retrieve a textual representation of a reason for a
symbolization failure.

Signed-off-by: Daniel M眉ller <deso@posteo.net>
